    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't get why it's so dangerous if it's just a juice. i'm a big person and i take my meds at a specific time, so couldn't i just wait a few hours after taking the pill before I drink the juice? like, if I space them out, wouldn't that solve the enzyme thing you're talking about?",
